HEADWORD: Effluent
<hw>Ef"flu*ent</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <ety>[L.
<ets>effluens</ets>, <ets>-entis</ets>, p. pr. of <ets>effluere</ets> to
