[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Effluent</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Effluent
<hw>Ef"flu*ent</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Geog.)</fld> <def>A stream that
flows out of another stream or lake.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

